        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "なになに『圧倒的な輝き、キセキの舞台』か。\r\n相変わらず眩しいな。",
            "enText": "What's this? \"A blinding light, the stage of \nmiracles…\" As radiant as ever, I see…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": 1000175762482836925,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "でも、私も負けないぞ！",
            "enText": "But I shall not be overshadowed!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": 6679595741830141033,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "ターフの上で最高のショーを……\r\nそう決めたからね。",
            "enText": "I swore I would give the crowd \nthe show of a lifetime… and I \nintend to keep that promise.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": -8747616812621955806,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "憧れるだけの少女はもういない。\r\n私は前に進むよ――お母さん。",
            "enText": "I'm no longer that little girl watching you go. \nI'm forging my own path now… Mother.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": -1793924811131472517,
            "blockIdx": 4
        }
